com.tractrac.subscription.lib.api.competitor

Interface ICompetitorsListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISubscriberListener

    public interface ICompetitorsListener
extends ISubscriberListener

    This listener is used to receive events related with the competitor list. It is used at a IEventSubscriber level: it means that it is not necessary to be subscribed to an individual race to receive its events.

    Author:
    Jorge Piera Llodrá
